sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    actor U as User
    participant W as Browser<br/>(web-app)
    participant API as Identity Core API<br/>(api.fivucsas.com)
    participant BIO as Biometric Service<br/>(internal-only)

    note over U,W: Face enrollment -- CLIENT-SIDE-EMBEDDING path (production default)

    U->>W: start face enrollment
    W->>W: getUserMedia capture --<br/>MediaPipe FaceLandmarker (478 pts)
    W->>W: quality pre-gate + ADVISORY passive PAD<br/>(MiniFASNet, onnxruntime-web)
    W->>W: compute Facenet512 embedding IN-BROWSER<br/>(onnxruntime-web, L2-normalized 512-d vector)
    note right of W: RAW IMAGE NEVER LEAVES THE DEVICE --<br/>only the irreversible 512-float vector is sent<br/>(data minimization)

    W->>API: POST /api/v1/biometric/enroll-embedding/userId<br/>{embedding(512), quality, padScore},<br/>Bearer JWT, X-Request-Nonce
    API->>API: edge + filter gates: Traefik TLS,<br/>rate limit, anti-replay nonce<br/>(Redis, 5-min TTL), JWT auth,<br/>RBAC biometric:enroll or self,<br/>tenant scope

    API->>BIO: POST /api/v1/enroll-embedding<br/>{512-vector}, X-API-Key,<br/>Docker network only
    note over BIO: continues in part (b):<br/>validate dimension, store template
